ness%20acumen.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20sees%20%26quot%3Bseveral%20ways%26quot%3B%20generative%20AI%20can%20make%20money%2C%20and%20laid%20out%20three%20specific%20paths%20to%20this%20becoming%20%26quot%3Ba%20massive%20business%26quot%3B%20for%20Meta.%20Although%20getting%20there%20is%20a%20%26quot%3Blong-term%26quot%3B%20prospect%2C%20he%20warned.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E%26quot%3BBusiness%20messaging%26quot%3B%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EOne%20of%20the%20ways%20AI%20can%20make%20money%20is%20by%20building%20up%20%26quot%3Bbusiness%20messaging%2C%26quot%3B%20where%20companies%20pay%20Meta%20for%20generative%20AI%20tools%2C%20such%20as%20services%20that%20support%20automated%20interactions%20with%20users%20and%20customers.%20Zuckerberg%20envisions%20Meta's%20AI%20moving%20beyond%20just%20being%20a%20chatbot%20and%20becoming%20an%20AI%20%26quot%3Bagent%26quot%3B%20that%20handles%20more%20complex%20tasks%2C%20and%20processes%20multiple%20queries%20to%20solve%20user%20problems%2C%20instead%20of%20coming%20back%20instantly%20with%20rote%20answers.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ERevenue%20from%20AI%20business%20messaging%20is%20%26quot%3Bone%20of%20the%20nearer%20term%20opportunities%2C%26quot%3B%20Zuckerberg%20said.%20While%20it%20may%20not%20become%20a%20reality%20this%20year%2C%20he%20noted%20that%20it's%20less%20than%20five%20years%20away.%20The%20immediate%20goal%20on%20this%20front%20is%20to%20%26quot%3Bget%20many%20hundreds%20of%20millions%20or%20billions%20of%20people%20to%20use%20Meta%20AI%20as%20a%20core%20part%20of%20what%20they%20do%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20explained.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3EAds%20appearing%20in%20%26quot%3BAI%20interactions%26quot%3B%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EAnother%20way%20generative%20AI%20could%20make%20money%20for%20Meta%20is%20by%20%26quot%3Bintroducing%20ads%20or%20paid%20content%20into%20AI%20interactions%2C%26quot%3B%20Zuckerberg%20said.%20Although%20brands%20and%20companies%20paying%20for%20products%20to%20show%20up%20in%20generative%20AI%20results%20is%20not%20yet%20the%20standard%20for%20AI%20chatbots%2C%20Meta's%20entire%20business%20is%20effectively%20driven%20by%20selling%20digital%20advertising.%20Inserting%20ads%20into%20its%20social%20and%20messaging%20products%20is%20at%20the%20core%20of%20Meta%20as%20a%20company.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAI%20is%20already%20being%20more%20widely%20deployed%20by%20Meta%20in%20its%20newer%20%26quot%3Bunconnected%20content%26quot%3B%20algorithm%20for%20social%20content%20recommendations%2C%20which%20Zuckerberg%20said%20is%20leading%20to%20more%20app%20engagement.%20That%2C%20in%20turn%2C%20leads%20to%20more%20people%20seeing%20more%20ads.%20Right%20now%2C%2030%25%20of%20the%20content%20Facebook%20users%20see%20is%20recommended%20by%20AI%2C%20and%20the%20same%20goes%20for%2050%25%20of%20the%20content%20seen%20by%20Instagram%20users%2C%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3ESelling%20access%20to%20AI%20models%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EA%20third%20distinct%20way%20Meta%20may%20make%20money%20from%20AI%20is%20by%20selling%20access%20to%20models%20as%20they%20get%20larger.%20%26quot%3BEnabling%20people%20to%20pay%20to%20use%20bigger%20AI%20models%20and%20access%20more%20compute%2C%26quot%3B%20as%20Zuckerberg%20put%20it%20on%20Wednesday.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ERight%20now%2C%20Llama%203%20and%20the%20Meta's%20other%20large%20language%20models%20are%20freely%20available%20to%20users%20and%20companies%20below%20a%20certain%20size%20threshold.%20Charging%20for%20access%20might%20be%20a%20move%20away%20from%20Meta's%20%26quot%3Bopen%20source%26quot%3B%20approach%20here.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BSo%20if%20the%20technology%20and%20products%20evolve%20in%20the%20way%20that%20we%20hope%2C%20each%20of%20those%20will%20unlock%20massive%20amounts%20of%20value%20for%20people%20and%20business%20for%20us%20over%20time%2C%26quot%3B%20Zuckerberg%20said.%20%26quot%3BI%20think%20it%20makes%20sense%20to%20go%20for%20it%2C%20and%20we're%20going%20to.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsid