and%20track%20her%20spending.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EThe%20easiest%20way%20for%20saving%20to%20become%20a%20habit%20is%20to%20automate%20your%20saving%20and%20then%20increase%20it%20over%20time.%C2%A0%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fmillennialindebt.com%2Fabout%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EMelissa%20Jean-Baptiste%3C%2Fa%3E%20writes%20in%20her%20book%2C%20%26quot%3B%3Cspan%3ESo%20%E2%80%A6%20This%20Is%20Why%20I'm%20Broke%3C%2Fspan%3E%2C%26quot%3B%20%26quot%3Bsaving%20money%20is%20a%20skill%20that%20requires%20practice%20and%20steady%20financial%20habits.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EJean-Baptiste%2C%20who%20paid%20off%20over%20%24100%2C000%20of%20student%20loan%20debt%2C%20has%20seven%20bank%20accounts%3A%20one%20for%20each%20savings%20bucket%20in%20her%20budget.%20It%20helps%20her%20keep%20her%20money%20organized%20and%20works%20well%20for%20her%20financial%20goals.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDo%20we%20all%20need%20seven%20bank%20accounts%3F%20Jean-Baptiste%20advises%20no.%20%26quot%3BWhat%20you%20need%20is%20exactly%20what%20supports%20the%20routines%20and%20habits%20you%20created%20to%20support%20your%20financial%20goals%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20writes.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20beauty%20of%20personal%20finance%20is%20that%20it's%20personal.%20Jean-Baptiste%20opened%20seven%20bank%20accounts%20to%20help%20her%20watch%20her%20money.%20%26quot%3BI%20monitored%20and%20tracked%20how%20much%20money%20was%20going%20in%20and%20out%20of%20%3Cem%3Eeach%20%3C%2Fem%3Ecategory%20in%20my%20budget.%20Having%20just%20one%20account%20with%20all%20my%20savings%20in%20one%20place%20didn't%20work%20for%20me%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20writes.%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20important%20thing%20about%20saving%20is%20getting%20started%20and%20creating%20a%20habit.%20You%20have%20to%20cultivate%20the%20habit%20of%20saving.%20I%20always%20say%20to%20set%20it%20and%20forget%20it.%20Make%20saving%20a%20financial%20habit%20and%20a%20part%20of%20your%20routine.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHere%20are%20a%20few%20steps%20you%20can%20take%20to%20save%20more%20money%3A%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3E1.%20Set%20up%20the%20bank%20accounts%20that%20you%20need%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EJean-Baptiste%20writes%2C%20%26quot%3BIf%20you're%20just%20getting%20started%20saving%2C%20or%20you're%20reconditioning%20your%20routines%20and%20financial%20habits%2C%20three%20accounts%20is%20a%20good%20place%20to%20start.%20A%20checking%20account%20for%20your%20day%20to%20day%20expenses%20and%20bills%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fpersonal-finance%2Fwhat-is-an-emergency-fund%5C%22%3Eemergency%20savings%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20house%20three%20to%20six%20months%20of%20expenses%2C%20and%20discretionary%20savings%20for%20anything%20you%20may%20be%20planning%20on%20purchasing.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20totally%20agree.%20I%20actually%20have%20five%20accounts%3A%20checking%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fpersonal-finance%2Fbest-high-yield-savings-accounts-rates-right-now%5C%22%3Ehigh-yield%20savings%20account%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20a%20travel%20account%2C%20a%20business%20account%2C%20and%20an%20account%20for%20a%20down%20payment%20on%20a%20home.%20I%20have%20automatic%20deductions%20that%20go%20into%20savings%20and%20the%20home%20account%2C%20and%20I%20deposit%20money%20into%20the%20business%20and%20travel%20accounts%20as%20needed.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Caside%3E%3Cp%3EAccounts%20like%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fpersonal-finance%2Fsofi-checking-savings-review%5C%22%3ESoFi%20Checking%20and%20Savings%3C%2Fa%3E%20can%20be%20great%20account%20options%20if%20you%20want%20to%20keep%20your%20savings%20and%20checking%20under%20one%20account.%20SoFi%20offers%20Money%20Vaults%2C%20a%20tool%20that%20can%20help%20you%20save%20for%20individual%20goals.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Faside%3E%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3E2.%20Pay%20yourself%20first%20every%20paychec