0to%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Fpets%2Fbest-self-cleaning-litter-boxes%5C%22%3Ebest%20self-cleaning%20litter%20boxes%3C%2Fa%3E.%20For%20weeks%2C%20I%20took%20notes%20as%20my%20cats%20circled%2C%20dug%2C%20and%20did%20their%20business%2C%20and%20in%20the%20end%2C%20I%20selected%20Litter-Robot%204%20as%20the%20best%20overall%20self-cleaning%20box.%20Sure%2C%20%24699%20is%20a%20lot%20to%20spend%20on%20a%20litter%20box%2C%20but%20this%20machine%20gets%20the%20job%20done.%20It%20automatically%20disposes%20of%20cat%20waste%2C%20sparing%20me%20from%20having%20to%20see%20or%20smell%20it%2C%20and%20it%20keeps%20my%20cats%20from%20stepping%20in%20it%20later.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Litter-Robot%204%20also%20has%20the%20best%20safety%20features%20of%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Fpets%2Fbest-litter-box%5C%22%3Ebest%20litter%20boxes%3C%2Fa%3E%20I've%20tested.%20It%20cycles%20quietly%20and%20is%20thoughtfully%20designed%20for%20cats%20of%20all%20sizes%20and%20needs%20with%20a%20spacious%20interior%20for%20large%20cats%20and%20optional%20steps%20for%20felines%20with%20limited%20mobility.%20Plus%2C%20its%20smart%20features%20can%20help%20you%20monitor%20your%20cat's%20well-being.%20The%20box%20is%20available%20in%20white%20or%20black%2C%20and%20I%20have%20it%20in%20both%20colors%2C%20which%20were%20provided%20to%20me%20as%20review%20samples%20by%20the%20brand.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-label%3D%5C%22Design%20and%20specs%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EDesign%20and%20specs%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EA%20self-cleaning%20litter%20box%20has%20two%20main%20jobs%3A%20It%20makes%20your%20life%20easier%2C%20and%20it%20keeps%20your%20cat's%20box%20more%20sanitary.%20The%20Litter-Robot%204%20accomplishes%20these%20tasks%20with%20an%20auto-cycling%20globe%20that%20separates%20clean%20litter%20from%20waste%20and%20deposits%20clumps%20into%20a%20drawer%20below.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20paws%20of%20a%20gray%20and%20white%20cat%20sitting%20inside%20the%20Litter-Robot%204%20are%20visible%20just%20above%20the%20white%20pull-out%20waste%20bin.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F64cd39f58df5080019d32770%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22900%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EYou%20can%20use%20the%20waste%20bin%20with%20or%20without%20a%20liner.%3Cp%3EJanelle%20Leeson%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Litter-Robot%204%20improves%20on%20the%20brand's%20previous%20generations%20with%20an%20upgraded%20laser%20sensing%20system%20and%20an%20extra-large%20waste%20drawer%20with%20odor-locking%20technology.%20The%20third%20generation%20machine%20can%20recognize%20cats%20weighing%205%20pounds%20or%20more%2C%20but%20the%20Litter-Robot%204's%20laser%20sensing%20system%20can%20recognize%20cats%20weighing%20at%20least%203%20pounds.%20The%20larger%2C%20odor-reducing%20waste%20drawer%20requires%20less%20frequent%20emptying.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThis%20box%20has%20a%20very%20quiet%20cycle%20of%20about%2033%20decibels%20(dB).%20It's%20significantly%20quieter%20than%20the%20Litter-Robot%203%20(48.7%20dB)%20and%20our%20dust-free%20recommendation%2C%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Faffiliate.insider.com%3FamazonTrackingID%3Dbiauto-61035-20%26h%3D8bbfc13a76a55eb4907a921f03098f1ff686482c740ec78889c3407dca16811f%26postID%3D64cd3882cfd91a08ec45eaea%26postSlug%3Dguides%252Fpets%252Fwhisker-litter-robot-4-review%26site%3Dbi%26u%3Dhttps%253A%252F%252Fwww.amazon.com%252FCatGenie-A-I-Self-Washing-Cat-Box%252Fdp%252FB082XGNZC7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ECatGenie%20AI%3C%2Fa%3E%20(51.4%20dB).%20A%20difference%20of%2015%20dB%20is%20significant%20when%20you%20live%20in%20a%20small%20space%20or%20if%2C%20like%20me%2C%20you%20keep%20the%20litter%20box%20in%20a%20bedroom.%20For%20the%20sake%20of%20comparison%2C%20the%20sound%20of%20a%20whisper%