2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Litter-Robot%204%20arrives%20almost%20fully%20assembled%20in%20a%20large%20box.%20I%20plugged%20it%20in%2C%20added%20our%20favorite%20clumping%20litter%2C%20and%20followed%20the%20step-by-step%20setup%20guide%20in%20the%20app.%20My%20cats%20had%20plenty%20of%20experience%20using%20the%20Litter-Robots%202%20and%203%2C%20so%20they%20took%20to%20the%20new%20box%20right%20away.%20Insider%20Reviews%20senior%20reporter%20James%20Brains%20also%20tested%20the%20Litter-Robot%204%2C%20and%20his%20cats%20began%20using%20the%20automatic%20box%20exclusively%20after%20four%20days%20of%20encouragement.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20like%20that%20when%20I%20open%20the%20app%2C%20all%20my%20current%20Litter-Robot%20devices%20are%20visible%2C%20including%20our%20Litter-Robot%20Feeder.%20The%20home%20screen%20shows%20how%20full%20the%20waste%20drawer%20is%2C%20and%20with%20one%20click%2C%20I%20can%20check%20the%20weight%20of%20the%20last%20cat%20who%20used%20the%20box%2C%20when%20the%20box%20last%20cycled%2C%20and%20how%20much%20clean%20litter%20remains.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20side%20by%20side%20of%20a%20screenshot%20of%20the%20app%20next%20to%20a%20black%20and%20white%20cat%20with%20the%20Litter-Robot%20in%20background.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F64cd3d0b8df5080019d32bf2%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22900%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20Whisker%20app%20provides%20plenty%20of%20information%20about%20your%20cat's%20usage.%3Cp%3EJanelle%20Leeson%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EBecause%20I%20have%20more%20than%20one%20litter%20box%2C%20I%20empty%20the%20Litter-Robot%20waste%20drawer%20roughly%20once%20a%20month%20and%20top%20off%20the%20clean%20litter%20even%20less%20frequently.%20The%20unit%20comes%20with%20a%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Faffiliate.insider.com%3FamazonTrackingID%3Dbiauto-61035-20%26h%3D23bf27a0e14f4c5707d90c38f23ba0d492862081da9b34a459d2300b51fb2a97%26postID%3D64cd3882cfd91a08ec45eaea%26postSlug%3Dguides%252Fpets%252Fwhisker-litter-robot-4-review%26site%3Dbi%26u%3Dhttps%253A%252F%252Fwww.litter-robot.com%252Flitter-robot%252Faccessories%252Flitter-robot-4-fence.html%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eremovable%20fence%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20prevent%20litter%20scatter%2C%20but%20for%20good%20measure%2C%20I%20pair%20it%20with%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Faffiliate.insider.com%3FamazonTrackingID%3Dbiauto-61035-20%26h%3D01b18fa8cc29ef2b378df099720db719ef5940896c939ad4eaa687e58be4d538%26postID%3D64cd3882cfd91a08ec45eaea%26postSlug%3Dguides%252Fpets%252Fwhisker-litter-robot-4-review%26site%3Dbi%26u%3Dhttps%253A%252F%252Fwww.litter-robot.com%252Flitter-robot%252Faccessories%252Flitter-robot-litter-trap-mat.html%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EWhisker's%20litter%20trap%20mat%3C%2Fa%3E.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20machine%20automatically%20cycles%20waste%20into%20its%20waste%20bin%20after%20every%20use.%20But%20our%20experts%20and%20the%20brand%20say%20every%20litter%20box%20requires%20an%20occasional%20deep%20cleaning.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETo%20deep%20clean%20the%20Litter-Robot%2C%20I%20press%20the%20%26quot%3BEmpty%26quot%3B%20button%20on%20the%20unit%20panel%20to%20empty%20the%20litter%20into%20the%20waste%20drawer.%20Then%20I%20remove%20the%20approximately%208-pound%20globe%20and%20wash%20it%20with%20soap%20and%20water%20in%20the%20bathtub%20or%20outside%20with%20a%20hose.%20The%20brand%20recommends%20a%20deep%20clean%20every%20one%20to%20three%20months.%20If%20you%20notice%20waste%20sticking%20to%20the%20sides%20of%20the%20globe%2C%20like%20our%20tester%20Brains%2C%20I%20recommend%20deep%20cleaning%20more%20often.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20Litter%20Robot%204%20disassembled%20with%20its%20parts%20laying%20on%20either%20side%20of%20it.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F64cd3dba20f1cf0019cad86f%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22900%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EIt%20is%20easy%20to%20disassemble%20the%20Litter-Robot%204%20for%20deep%20cleaning.%3Cp%3EJanelle%20Leeson%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EOne%20major%20way%20Whisker%20stands%20out%20from%20its%20competitors%3A%20You%20can%20reach%20a%20human%20in%20their%20customer%20service%20department.%20While%20I%20struggled%20to%20find%20phone%20numbers%20for%20other%20brands%2C%20I've%20spoken%20to%20customer%20service%20reps%20a%20few%20times%20about%20the%20faulty%20pinch%20detection%20in%20our%20Litter-Robot%203.%20(Rest%20assured%2C%20this%20is%20no%20longer%20an%20issue%20in%20the%20Litter-Robot%204.)%20Generally%2C%20the%20reps%20resolve%20any%20issues%20by%20accessing%20my%20machine's%20performance%20history%20and%20information%2C%20allowing%20them%20to%20quickly%20pinpoint%20the%20problem.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-label%3D%5C%22The%20cons%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EThe%20cons%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EThere's%20no%20denying%20that%20the%20Litter-Robot%204%20is%20expensive.%20However%2C%20you%20have%20three%20months%20to%20return%20it%20if%20your%20cat%20doesn't%20want%20to%20make%20the%20switch.%20You'll%20just%20have%20to%20pay%20for%20shipping.%20The%20machine%20also%20comes%20with%20a%20one-year%20warranty%20covering%20accidental%20damage%2C%20power%20surges%2C%20mechanical%20and%20electrical%20breakdowns%2C%20and%20software%20support.%20If%20you%20need%20to%20send%20your%20unit%20back%20to%20Whisker%20for%20mechanical%20issues%20during%20the%20warranty%20period%2C%20the%20brand%20will%20cover%20shipping%20both%20ways.%20You%20also%20have%20the%20option%20to%20purchase%20an%20extended%20three-year%20plan%20for%20%24100.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20haven't%20had%20to%20use%20my%20warranty%20for%20the%20Litter-Robot%204%2C%20but%20that%20doesn't%20mean%20it's%20perfect.%20For%20example%2C%20at%20one%20point%20the%20unit%20cycled%20whether%20a%20cat%20had%20used%20it%20or%20not.%20Whisker%20has%20since%20pushed%20a%20software%20update%20to%20fix%20the%20issue.%20%3Cstrong%3E%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EYou%20also%20need%20to%20place%20the%20unit%20on%20a%20hard%20surface%20(not%20carpet)%20to%20accurately%20weigh%20your%20cat.%20Whisker%20just%20released%20a%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Faffiliate.insider.com%3FamazonTrackingID%3Dbiauto-61035-20%26h%3D7c245e4873fc8c5dfa317e5ddf6e883e9da22547a556fe5e958fc426d63a0af3%26postID%3D64cd3882cfd91a08ec45eaea%26postSlug%3Dguides%252Fpets%252Fwhisker-litter-robot-4-review%26site%3Dbi%26u%3Dhttps%253A%252F%252Fwww.litter-robot.com%252Flitter-robot-4-carpet-tray.html%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ELitter-Robot%204%20Carpet%20Tray%3C%2Fa%3E%20(%2430)%2C%20but%20our%20unit%20currently%20sits%20on%20a%20makeshift%20platform.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBrains%20also%20says%20he%20received%20cleaning%20notifications%20before%20they%20seemed%20necessary%2C%20but%20that%20the%20sensor%20resets%20when%20he%20shakes%20the%20drawer%20to%20distribute%20the%20waste%20more%20evenly.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-label%3D%5C%22What%20are%20your%20alternatives%3F%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EWhat%20are%20your%20alternatives%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EWith%20all%20the%20bells%20and%20whistles%20it%20includes%2C%20the%20Litter-Robot%204%20is%20a%20worthwhile%20smart%20home%20device.%20If%20you%20don't%20need%20a%20self-cleaning%20litter%20box%20with%20smart%20features%2C%20I%20recommend%20the%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Faffiliate.insider.com%3FamazonTrackingID%3Dbiauto-61035-20%26h%3D68d6f0bf02349184aabba09a6b4044705c7f3d3170a36f26565ca090313eec93%26postID%3D64cd3882cfd91a08ec45eaea%26postSlug%3Dguides%252Fpets%252Fwhisker-litter-robot-4-review%26site%3Dbi%26u%3Dhttps%253A%252F%252Fwww.chewy.com%252Fpetsafe-scoopfree-original-automatic%252Fdp%252F227655%5C%22%20target%3