es-to-reflect-on-future%2Farticleshow%2F109572376.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia-indiatimes-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Feurope%2Fspains-sanchez-suspends-public-duties-to-reflect-on-future%2Famp_articleshow%2F109572376.cms%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Feurope%2Fspains-sanchez-suspends-public-duties-to-reflect-on-future%2Famp_articleshow%2F109572376.cms%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22%26quot%3BBJP%20Reading%20Manifesto%20Written%20By%20Ghosts%3F%26quot%3B%20P%20Chidambaram%20On%20Mangalsutra%20Jab%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EHitting%20back%20at%20the%20BJP%20and%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%20over%20their%20claims%20that%20his%20party%20intends%20to%20redistribute%20wealth%20and%20that%20even%20women's%20%3Cem%3E'mangalsutras'%3C%2Fem%3E%20were%20under%20threat%2C%20Congress%20leader%20P%20Chidambaram%20has%20challenged%20them%20to%20show%20even%20one%20mention%20of%20any%20such%20promise%20in%20the%20manifesto.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Chidambaram%20also%20said%20such%20claims%20were%20possibly%20being%20made%20because%20his%20party's%20manifesto%20was%20a%20well-considered%20one%20while%20the%20BJP's%20was%20a%20document%20of%20cult%20worship.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESpeaking%20exclusively%20to%20NDTV%20on%20Wednesday%2C%20the%20head%20of%20Congress'%20manifesto%20committee%2C%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BAll%20that%20the%20BJP%20has%20been%20saying%20for%20the%20past%20three%20or%20four%20days%2C%20especially%20from%20the%20Prime%20Minister%20downwards%2C%20is%20absolute%20rubbish.%20Show%20me%20one%20word%20called%20redistribution%20anywhere%20in%20the%20manifesto%2C%20which%20runs%20to%2045%20pages.%20Show%20me%20the%20phrase%20'%20redistribute%20the%20wealth'%20anywhere.%20Unless%20they%20are%20reading%20a%20manifesto%20written%20by%20ghosts%2C%20hired%20by%20the%20BJP%2C%20in%20invisible%20ink%3B%20it's%20not%20in%20our%20manifesto.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETo%20a%20question%20on%20Sam%20Pitroda%2C%20Chairman%20of%20the%20Overseas%20Congress%2C%20stirring%20up%20a%20controversy%20by%20terming%20the%20inheritance%20law%20in%20the%20US%20%26quot%3Binteresting%26quot%3B%2C%20the%20former%20finance%20minister%20only%20said%20that%20it%20does%20not%20appear%20in%20the%20manifesto%20and%20that%20he%20himself%20had%20not%20spoken%20about%20it.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E'Completely%20Imaginary'%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20the%20PM's%20claim%20that%20the%20Congress%20planned%20to%20give%20reservation%20to%20Muslims%20at%20the%20expense%20of%20Scheduled%20Castes%2C%20Scheduled%20Tribes%20and%20OBCs%2C%20Mr%20Chidambaram%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BWhere%20is%20that%20in%20the%20manifesto%3F%20All%20the%20statements%20made%20by%20the%20BJP%20leaders%20in%20the%20last%20four%20days%20are%20completely%20imaginary.%20They%20must%20show%20where%20this%20is%20in%20the%20manifesto.%20I%20have%20been%20challenging%20them%20publicly.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20former%20finance%20minister%20asserted%20that%20the%20Congress%20has%20done%20its%20math%20and%20is%20confident%20that%20every%20promise%20made%20in%20its%20manifesto%20can%20be%20fulfilled%20over%20the%20term%20of%20a%20government.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BLast%20time%2C%20when%20we%20said%20we%20would%20waive%20agricultural%20loans%2C%20we%20were%20ridiculed%20and%20told%20that%20there%20is%20no%20money%2C%20but%20our%20government%20waived%20such%20loans%20to%20the%20tune%20of%20Rs%2060%2C000%20crore.%20When%20we%20started%20the%20Mahatma%20Gandhi%20Rural%20Employment%20Guarantee%20Scheme%2C%20we%20were%20again%20asked%2C%20'Where%20is%20the%20money%3F'%2C%20but%20we%20implemented%20it%20and%20the%20BJP%20has%20continued%20it.%20We%20found%20the%20money%20for%20it%2C%20and%20so%20has%20the%20BJP%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEmphasising%20that%20the%20Congress%20manifesto%2C%20which%20promises%20justice%20to%2