0challenge%20the%20bill.s%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThis%20is%20the%20beginning%2C%20not%20the%20end%20of%20this%20long%20process%2C%26quot%3B%20TikTok%20told%20staff%20on%20Saturday%2C%20Reuters%20previously%20reported.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThis%20unconstitutional%20law%20is%20a%20TikTok%20ban%2C%20and%20we%20will%20challenge%20it%20in%20court%2C%26quot%3B%20a%20spokesperson%20said%20on%20Wednesday.%20%26quot%3BWe%20believe%20the%20facts%20and%20the%20law%20are%20clearly%20on%20our%20side%2C%20and%20we%20will%20ultimately%20prevail.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20company%20did%20not%20respond%20to%20a%20request%20for%20further%20comment.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ERIVALS%20ON%20THE%20HUNT%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOther%20tech%20platforms%20are%20waiting%20in%20the%20wings%20for%20TikTok's%20users%20and%20ad%20revenue.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EYouTube%20has%20been%20particularly%20aggressive%20in%20going%20after%20TikTok%20marketing%20budgets%2C%20asking%20ad%20agencies%20to%20test%20one%20of%20its%20advertising%20products%20to%20see%20how%20it%20performs%20against%20TikTok%20specifically%2C%20according%20to%20one%20advertising%20agency%20director%2C%20who%20declined%20to%20be%20named%20to%20discuss%20conversations%20with%20the%20platforms.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERecent%20surveys%20have%20shown%20that%20Gen-Z%20are%20increasingly%20using%20TikTok%20to%20search%20for%20information%20and%20businesses%20rather%20than%20Google.%20Google%20did%20not%20respond%20to%20request%20for%20comment.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESpotify%20CEO%20Daniel%20Ek%20told%20investors%20on%20Tuesday%20that%20short-form%20video%20content%20is%20%26quot%3Ba%20big%20focus%20of%20ours%2C%26quot%3B%20which%20would%20make%20its%20way%20to%20the%20service's%20music%20streaming%20product%20in%202024.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEven%20with%20their%20commitment%20to%20the%20platform%2C%20advertisers%20are%20beginning%20to%20shift%20from%20their%20theoretical%20contingency%20plans%2C%20which%