s.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20report%20on%20this%20patient%20was%20prepared%20by%20PhD%20candidate%20Magda%20Vergouwe%2C%20Centre%20for%20Experimental%20and%20Molecular%20Medicine%20(CEMM)%2C%20Amsterdam%20University%20Medical%20Centre%20(Amsterdam%20UMC)%2C%20University%20of%20Amsterdam%2C%20Netherlands%2C%20and%20colleagues.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThis%20case%20underscores%20the%20risk%20of%20persistent%20SARS-CoV-2%20infections%20in%20immunocompromised%20individuals%20as%20unique%20SARS-CoV-2%20viral%20variants%20may%20emerge%20due%20to%20extensive%20intra-host%20evolution.%20We%20emphasise%20the%20importance%20of%20continuing%20genomic%20surveillance%20of%20SARS-CoV-2%20evolution%20in%20immunocompromised%20individuals%20with%20persistent%20infections%20given%20the%20potential%20public%20health%20threat%20of%20possibly%20introducing%20viral%20escape%20variants%20into%20the%20community%2C%26quot%3B%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.scimex.org%2Fnewsfeed%2Fthis-poor-soul-had-covid-19-for-almost-2-years-so-long-it-mutated-into-a-new-variant%5C%22%3EMagda%20Vergouwe%20and%20colleagues%20said%20in%20a%20statement.%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20study%20emphasises%20how%20pre-existing%20illnesses%20and%20treatments%20that%20suppress%20the%20immune%20system%20can%20create%20a%20breeding%20ground%20for%20long-term%20infections%20and%20potentially%20new%20viral%20variants.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20duration%20of%20SARS-CoV-2%20infection%20in%20this%20described%20case%20is%20extreme%2C%20but%20prolonged%20infections%20in%20immunocompromised%20patients%20are%20much%20more%20common%20compared%20to%20the%20general%20community.%20Further%20work%20by%20our%20team%20includes%20describing%20a%20cohort%20of%20prolonged%20infections%20in%20immunocompromised%20patients%20from%20our%20hospital%2C%20with%20infection%20durations%20varying%20between%201%20month%20and%202%20years.%20However%2C%20from%20the%20viewpoint%20of%20the%20general%20public%2C%20prolonged%20infections%20remain%20rare%20as%20the%20immunocompromised%20population%20is%20only%20a%20very%20small%20percentage%20of%20the%20total%20population%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20authors%20said%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.scimex.org%2Fnewsfeed%2Fthis-poor-soul-had-covid-19-for-almost-2-years-so-long-it-mutated-into-a-new-variant%5C%22%3Ein%20a%20statement.%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1713979560000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-01%2Fd31ktkno_covid-19-_625x300_11_January_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fscience%2Fthis-man-had-covid-19-for-almost-2-years-so-long-it-mutated-into-a-new-variant-5515656%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Despite%20being%20vaccinated%2C%20his%20compromised%20immune%20system%20couldn't%20fully%20fend%20off%20the%20virus%2C%20leading%20to%20severe%20complications.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fscience%2Fthis-man-had-covid-19-for-almost-2-years-so-long-it-mutated-into-a-new-variant-5515656%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fscience%2Fthis-man-had-covid-19-for-almost-2-years-so-long-it-mutated-into-a-new-variant-5515656%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fscience%2Fthis-man-had-covid-19-for-almost-2-years-so-long-it-mutated-into-a-new-variant-5515656%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22%26quot%3BMake%20No%20Mistake%2C%20This%20Is%20A%20Ban%26quot%3B%3A%20TikTok%20Vows%20To%20Fight%20New%20US%20Law%20In%20Court%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3ETikTok's%20CEO%20vowed%20Wednesday%20to%20fight%20in%20the%20courts%20to%20overturn%20a%20newly%20signed%20US%20law%20that%20could%20see%20the%20popular%20app%20banned%20due%20to%20allegations%20it%20is%20controlled%20by%20the%20China%20government.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20legislation%20gives%20TikTok%20nine%20months%20to%20divest%20from%20its%20Chinese%20parent%20company%20ByteDance%20or%20be%20shut%20out%20of%20the%20American%20market.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20US%20and%20other%20Western%20officials%20have%20alleged%20the%20social%20media%20platform%20allows%20Beijing%20to%20collect%20data%20and%20spy%20on%20users.%20It%20has%20170%20million%20users%20in%20the%20United%20States%20alone%2C%20many%20of%20them%20young.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECritics%20say%20TikTok%20is%20also%20a%20conduit%20to%20spread%20propaganda.%20China%20and%20the%20company%20strongly%20deny%20the%20claims.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BMake%20no%20mistake%2C%20this%20is%20a%20ban.%20A%20ban%20on%20TikTok%20and%20a%20ban%20on%20you%20and%20your%20voice%2C%26quot%3B%20TikTok%20boss%20Shou%20Zi%20Chew%20said%20in%20a%20video%20posted%20on%20TikTok%20moments%20after%20President%20Joe%20Biden%20signed%20the%20bill%20into%20law.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BPoliticians%20may%20say%20otherwise%2C%20but%20don't%20get%20confused.%20Many%20who%20sponsored%20the%20bill%20admit%20a%20Tiktok%20ban%20is%20the%20ultimate%20goal.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EChew%20called%20the%20move%20%26quot%3Bironic%26quot%3B%20given%20that%20the%20%26quot%3Bfreedom%20of%20expression%20on%20TikTok%20reflects%20the%20same%20American%20values%20that%20make%20the%20United%20States%20a%20beacon%20of%20freedom.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BRest%20assured%2C%20we%20aren't%20going%20anywhere%2C%26quot%3B%20Chew%20told%20the%20platform's%20users.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20will%20keep%20fighting%20for%20your%20rights%20in%20the%20courts.%20The%20facts%20and%20the%20Constitution%20are%20on%20our%20side.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20ban%20measure%20was%20included%20in%20a%20%2495%20billion%20foreign%20aid%20package%2C%20including%20military%20assistance%20to%20Ukraine%2C%20Israel%20and%20Taiwan.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20bill%2C%20which%20could%20trigger%20the%20rare%20step%20of%20barring%20a%20company%20from%20operating%20in%20the%20US%20market%2C%20passed%20the%20Senate%20by%20a%2079