(UBT)%20chief%20Uddhav%20Thackeray%20for%20not%20attending%20the%20%3Cem%3E'Pran%20Pratishtha'%3C%2Fem%3E%20(consecration%20ceremony)%20of%20Ram%20Lalla%20at%20the%20Ayodhya%20temple%20and%20alleged%20that%20he%20turned%20down%20the%20invitation%20to%20the%20event%20due%20to%20'fear'%20of%20Congress%20leader%20Sonia%20Gandhi.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAmit%20Shah%2C%20while%20addressing%20a%20public%20rally%20in%20Maharashtra's%20Amaravati%20slammed%20the%20opposition%20leaders%2C%20including%20Congress%20MP%20Rahul%20Gandhi%20for%20not%20attending%20the%20event%20and%20accused%20them%20of%20%26quot%3Bhumiliating%26quot%3B%20Lord%20Ram.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BUddhav%20Thackeray%2C%20who%20claims%20to%20be%20the%20president%20of%20Shiv%20Sena%2C%20this%20fake%20president%20of%20Shiv%20Sena%20didn't%20attend%20the%20%3Cem%3E'Pran%20Pratishtha'%3C%2Fem%3E%20due%20to%20fear%20of%20Sonia%20Gandhi%20even%20after%20being%20invited.%20'Rahul%20Baba'%20too%20received%20the%20invitation%20but%20didn't%20attend%20the%20%3Cem%3E'Pran%20Pratishtha'%3C%2Fem%3E.%20These%20people%2C%20by%20not%20attending%20the%20%3Cem%3E'Pran%20Pratishtha'%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20have%20humiliated%20Lord%20Ram%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Shah%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDoubling%20down%20his%20charges%20against%20Uddhav%20Thackeray%2C%20the%20minister%20said%20that%20the%20former%20Maharashtra%20Chief%20Minister%20left%20every%20principle%20of%20Bal%20Thackeray%2C%20the%20Shiv%20Sena's%20patriarch.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BUmesh%20Kolhe%20was%20murdered%20and%20this%20so-called%20'Hindu%20%3Cem%3Ehit%20rakshak%3C%2Fem%3E'%20Uddhav%20Thackeray%20did%20nothing.%20'Uddhav%20babu'%2C%20you%20have%20left%20every%20enculturation%20of%20Balasaheb.%20I%20want%20to%20tell%20you%20that%20Eknath%20Shinde%20has%20moved%20forward%20with%20all%20the%20enculturation%20of%20Balasaheb.%20In%20Maharashtra%2C%20it's%20our%20govt%20now%2C%20it's%20the%20govt%20of%20Eknath%20Shinde%20and%20Devendra%20Fadnavis%2C%20and%20now%2C%