t%20month.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EInfina%20Finance%20Private%20Ltd%2C%20according%20to%20its%20website%2C%20was%20incorporated%20in%202008%20and%20is%20in%20the%20business%20of%20capital%20market%20financing%20and%20proprietary%20trading%20and%20investments.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EInfina%2C%20a%20non-deposit%20accepting%2C%20systemically%20important%20non-banking%20financial%20company%20registered%20with%20the%20RBI%2C%20had%20reported%20a%20profit%20of%20Rs%20105.55%20crore%20in%202022-23.%20The%20firm%20posted%20a%20total%20income%20of%20Rs%20227.84%20crore%20during%20the%20fiscal.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20Wednesday%2C%20the%20Reserve%20Bank%20of%20India%20(RBI)%20barred%20Kotak%20Mahindra%20Bank%20from%20onboarding%20new%20customers%20through%20its%20online%20and%20mobile%20banking%20channels%20and%20issuing%20fresh%20credit%20cards%20with%20immediate%20effect%20after%20the%20regulator%20found%20%26quot%3Bserious%20deficiencies%26quot%3B%20in%20the%20lender's%20IT%20risk%20management.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThese%20actions%2C%20the%20RBI%20said%2C%20are%20necessitated%20based%20on%20significant%20concerns%20arising%20out%20of%20the%20Reserve%20Bank's%20IT%20examination%20of%20the%20bank%20for%20the%20years%202022%20and%202023%2C%20and%20its%20continued%20failure%20to%20address%20these%20concerns%20in%20a%20comprehensive%20and%20timely%20manner.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1713975840000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.ndtvimg.com%2Fi%2F2016-08%2Fkotak-mahindra-bank-650-400_650x400_41471176025.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fkotak-mahindra-bank-promoter-infina-finance-donated-rs-60-crore-to-bjp-via-electoral-bonds-5515235%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Infina%20Finance%2C%20one%20of%20the%20promoter%20group%20entities%20of%20Kotak%20Mahindra%20B