and%20for%20this%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said%20smiling%20as%20he%20put%20a%20ring%20on%20her%20finger.%20The%20passengers%20in%20the%20plane%20cheered%20for%20the%20happy%20couple.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20airline%20wrote%20in%20the%20caption%2C%20%26quot%3BEngagement%20on%20board%20LOT!%20Captain%20Konrad%20proposed%20to%20Stewardess%20Paula%20during%20a%20flight%20to%20Krak%C3%B3w%2C%20the%20city%20where%20they%20first%20met.%20You%20won't%20see%20anything%20more%20touching%20today.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESince%20being%20shared%2C%20the%20post%20has%20amassed%20over%20two%20lakh%20views%20and%2016%2C000%20likes.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BBeautiful!%20Thank%20you%20LOT%20for%20sharing%20the%20beautiful%20stories%20of%20your%20employees%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20a%20user.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BTOTALLYYYYY%20LOVE%20IN%20THE%20AIR%2C%26quot%3B%20a%20person%20commented.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnother%20wrote%2C%20%26quot%3BHappiness%2C%20love%20and%20high%20flights!!%20What%20a%20great%20wedding%20proposal!%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BSafe%20travels%2C%20and%20enjoy%20your%20love%20and%20happiness%20in%20the%20years%20to%20come%2C%26quot%3B%20remarked%20a%20user.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20Facebook%20user%20added%2C%20%26quot%3BCongratulations%20to%20the%20couple%20in%20love.%20I%20wish%20you%20happiness%20and%20only%20sunny%20days%20and%20high%20flights%20together%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20love%20this!%20Sweet%20couple!%26quot%3B%20added%20another%20person.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1713972120000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-04%2F38ske6q8_lot-polish-airlines_625x300_24_April_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Foffbeat%2Fwatch-pilot-proposes-to-flight-attendant-on-poland-flight-internet-reacts-5514683%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Since%20being%20shared%2C%20the%20post%20has%20amassed%20over%20two%20lakh%20views%20and%2016%2C000%20likes.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement