01056_1.html%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Famp%2Fcompanies%2Fpeople%2Fpaytm-payments-bank-s-mukund-barsagade-joins-lendingkart-as-group-cfo-124042401056_1.html%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22India%20Had%20Its%20Own%20Inheritance%20Law%20Till%201985.%20Why%20It%20Was%20Abolished%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EIndian%20Overseas%20Congress%20chief%20Sam%20Pitroda's%20remarks%20on%20the%20US's%20inheritance%20tax%20have%20sparked%20a%20political%20whirlpool%20here%20in%20India%20amid%20the%20ongoing%20Lok%20Sabha%20elections.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Pitroda%20stirred%20up%20a%20massive%20controversy%20while%20countering%20the%20Prime%20Minister%20over%20his%20allegations%20that%20Congress%20plans%20to%20redistribute%20the%20nation's%20wealth%2C%20citing%20a%20US%20example%20of%20inheritance%20tax%20law.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIf%20a%20person%20has%20property%20worth%20US%20dollars%2010%20million%2C%20then%20after%20his%20death%2C%2045%20per%20cent%20of%20the%20property%20goes%20to%20his%20children%20and%2055%20per%20cent%20of%20the%20property%20goes%20to%20the%20government%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Pitroda%20told%20ANI%20and%20added%20that%20there%20is%20no%20such%20law%20in%20India.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BSuch%20issues%20should%20be%20discussed.%20We%20are%20talking%20about%20policies%20that%20are%20in%20the%20interest%20of%20the%20people%2C%20not%20just%20the%20rich%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EWhat%20is%20the%20Inheritance%20Tax%20law%20in%20US%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFirstly%2C%20the%20tax%20is%20not%20common%20in%20the%20US%20and%20is%20only%20in%20force%20in%20six%20states%20out%20of%20the%2050.%20The%20tax%20is%20imposed%20on%20the%20recipients%20who%20inherit%20assets%20of%20a%20person%20who%20has%20died.%20The%20taxation%20depends%20on%20the%20state%20in%20which%20the%20person%20lived%20or%20owned%20property.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThere's%20a%20stark%20difference%20between%20Estate%20Tax%20and%20Inheritance%20Tax%20in%20the%20US.%20The%20former%20is%20levied%20on%20the%20estate%20itself%20before%20it%20is%20distributed%2C%20while%20the%20latter%20is%20only%20against%20the%20beneficiaries.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EInheritance%20taxes%20are%20collected%20by%20six%20US%20states%3A%20Iowa%2C%20Kentucky%2C%20Maryland%2C%20Nebraska%2C%20New%20Jersey%2C%20and%20Pennsylvania.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EKey%20factors%20involved%20and%20how%20is%20it%20calculated%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20is%20not%20a%20Federal%20tax.%20It%20is%20levied%20based%20on%20the%20inheritor's%20relationship%20with%20the%20person%20and%20the%20value%20of%20the%20property.%20It%20is%20applied%20only%20to%20the%20portion%20of%20the%20inheritance%20which%20exceeds%20the%20exemption%20limit.%20Above%20the%20threshold%20limit%2C%20the%20tax%20is%20usually%20assessed%20on%20a%20sliding%20basis%20and%20the%20rates%20vary%20from%20single%20digits%20and%20can%20go%20up%20to%2018%25.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFor%20example%20in%20Pennsylvania%2C%20The%20tax%20rate%20is%204.5%25%20for%20transfers%20to%20direct%20descendants%20(lineal%20heirs)%2C%2012%25%20for%20transfers%20to%20siblings%2C%20and%2015%25%20for%20transfers%20to%20other%20heirs.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20Iowa%2C%20if%20the%20property%20is%20valued%20at%20less%20than%20%2425%2C000%20(Rs%2020.83%20lakh)%20then%20no%20tax%20is%20due.%20In%20Maryland%2C%20inheritances%20from%20estates%20smaller%20than%20%2450%2C000%20(Rs%2041.66%20lakh)%20are%20also%20exempt.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETo%20summarize%2C%20the%20closer%20an%20inheritor%20is%20to%20the%20asset%20owner%2C%20the%20lower%20the%20tax%20rate%20would%20be%20levied.%20In%20all%20six%20states%2C%20spouses%20of%20the%20owner%20are%20exempted.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20United%20Kingdom%2C%20a%2040%25%20inheritance%20tax%20is%20levied%20on%20assets%20worth%20over%20325%2C000%20pounds%20(Rs%203.37%20crore).%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EJapan%20has%20a%20high%20inheritance%20tax%20rate%20with%20the%20current%20highest%20rate%20standing%20at%2055%25.%20The%20rate%20is%20determined%20based%20on%20how%20much%20money%20is%20received%20by%20each%20statutory%20heir.%20Meanwhile%2C%20South%20Korea%20boasts%20a%2050%25%20inheritance%20tax%20rate.%20In%202021%2C%20The%20family%20of%20deceased%20Samsung%20Electronics%20chairman%20Lee%20Kun-hee%20said%20it%20would%20pay%20more%20than%2012%20trillion%20won%20(%2410.78%20billion)%20in%20inheritance%20taxes%20for%20the%20estate%20of%20the%20late%20patriarch.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EDid%20India%20Ever%20Have%20An%20Inheritance%20Tax%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAn%20inheritance%20tax%20law%20existed%20in%20India%20until%20former%20Prime%20Minister%20Rajiv%20Gandhi%20scrapped%20it%20in%201985.%20An%20Estate%20Duty%20was%20a%20form%20of%20tax%20that%20was%20calculated%20at%20the%20time%20of%20a%20person's%20death%2C%20it%20was%20introduced%20through%20the%20Estate%20Duty%20Act%2C%201953.%20It%20was%20payable%20only%20if%20the%20total%20value%20of%20the%20inherited%20portion%20of%20the%20property%20exceeded%20the%20exclusion%20limit.%20In%20India%2C%20it%20was%20set%20as%20high%20as%208%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.amsshardul.com%2Finsight%2Festate-duty-act-a-critical-analysis-of-the-journey-so-far%2F%5C%22%3E5%25%20on%20properties%3C%2Fa%3E.%20Properties%20worth%20at%20least%20Rs%201.5%20lakh%2C%20were%20taxed%20at%20a%20rate%20of%207.5%25.%20The%20objective%20was%20to%20narrow%20the%20income%20disparity%20but%20was%20scrapped%20in%201985.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAs%20both%20wealth-tax%20and%20estate%20duty%20laws%20apply%20to%20the%20property%20of%20a%20person%2C%20the%20former%20applying%20to%20his%20property%20before%20death%20and%20the%20latter%20after%20his%20death%2C%20the%20existence%20of%20two%20separate%20laws%20with%20reference%20to%20the%20same%20property%20amounts%20to%20procedural%20harassment%20to%20the%20taxpayers%20and%20the%20heirs%20of%20the%20deceased%20who%20have%20to%20comply%20with%20the%20provisions%20of%20two%20different%20laws.%20Having%20considered%20the%20relative%20merits%20of%20the%20two%20taxes%2C%20I%20am%20of%20the%20view%20that%20estate%20duty%20has%20not%20achieved%20the%20twin%20objectives%20with%20which%20it%20was%20introduced%2C%20namely%2C%20to%20reduce%20the%20unequal%20distribution%20of%20wealth%20and%20assist%20the%20States%20in%20financing%20their%20development%20schemes%2C%26quot%3B%20%C2%A0former%20Prime%20Minister%20VP%20Singh%2C%20who%20was%20the%20Finance%20Minister%20in%20Rajiv%20Gandhi's%20Cabinet%2C%20said%20in%20his%20budget%20speech.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhile%20the%20yield%20from%20estate%20duty%20is%20only%20about%20Rs.%2020%20crore%2C%20its%20cost%20of%20administration%20is%20relatively%20high.%20I%2C%20therefore%2C%20propose%20to%20abolish%20the%20levy%20of%20estate%20duty%20in%20respect%20of%20estates%20passing%20on%20deaths%20occurring%20on%20or%20after%2016%20March%201985.%20I%20come%20forward%20in%20due%20course%20with%20suitable%20legislation%20for%20this%20purpose%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20report%20by%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Feconomictimes.indiatimes.com%2Fnews%2Feconomy%2Fpolicy%2Fwhy-an-inheritance-tax-can-be-an-eminently-bad-idea%2Farticleshow%2F109568032.cms%3Ffrom%3Dmdr%5C%22%3EEconomic%20Times%3C%2Fa%3E%20states%20that%20India's%20inheritance%20tax%20was%20repealed%20in%201985%20because%20it%20neither%20helped%20bring%20down%20economic%20inequality%20in%20society%20nor%20did%20it%20contribute%20significantly%2C%20In%201984-85%2C%20the%20total%20tax%20collected%20under%20the%20Estate%20Duty%20Act%20was%20Rs%2020%20crore%2C%20but%20the%20cost%20of%20collection%20was%20very%20high%20because%20the%20complex%20calculation%20structure%20spawned%20a%20lot%20of%20litigation.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFor%20example%2C%20according%20to%20the%201980-81%20regular%20budget%2C%20the%20gross%20tax%20revenue%20in%20the%201979-80%20period%20was%20Rs%2011%2C447%20crore%2C%20out%20of%20which%20the%20Estate%20Duty%20contributed%20only%20Rs%2012%20crore%20which%20was%20later%20revised%20to%20Rs%2013%20crore%2C%20i.e%200.1%25%20of%20the%20total%20gross%20tax%20revenue.%20In%20the%20budget%2C%20the%20Estate%20Duty%20collection%20was%20projected%20to%20be%20the%20same%2C%20Rs%2013%20crore.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%201978-79%20budget%2C%20the%20Tax%20revenue%20in%20the%20previous%20budget%20was%20Rs%2010.75%20crore%20of%20the%20total%20revenue%20of%20Rs%209%2C005.46%20crore.%20The%20projection%20for%20the%201978-79%20budget%20was%20Rs%2011%20crore%20out%20of%20Rs%209%2C636%20crore%2C%20i.e.%200.1%25%20of%20the%20total%20tax%20revenue.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPoor%20implementation%20and%20loopholes%20in%20tax%20collection%20helped%20people%20avoid%20paying%20Estate%20Duty.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1713969420000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-04%2Fppbh8et8_sam-pitroda-inheritance-tax_625x300_24_April_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Findia-had-its-own-inheritance-law-till-1985-why-it-was-abolished-5514552%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Indian%20Overseas%20Congress%20chief%20Sam%20Pitroda's%20remarks%20on%20the%20US's%20inheritance%20tax%20have%20sparked%20a%20political%20whirlpool%20here%20in%20India%20amid%20the%20ongoing%20Lok%20Sabha%20elections.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Findia-had-its-own-inheritance-law-till-1985-why-it-was-abolished-5514552%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Findia-had-its-own-inheritance-law-till-1985-why-it-was-abolished-5514552%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Findia-had-its-own-inheritance-law-till-1985-why-it-was-abolished-5514552%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22%26quot%3BINDIA%20Bloc%20Busy%20Auctioning%20PM%20Chair%26quot%3B%3A%20PM's%20Fresh%20Strike%20On%20Opposition%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EPrime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%20on%20Wednesday%20said%20the%20opposition%20INDIA%20bloc%20is%20contemplating%20a%20%26quot%3Bone%20year%2C%20one%20PM%26quot%3B%20formula%20to%20resolve%20their%20leadership%20issue%20and%20added%20the%20world%20will%20ridicule%20such%20an%20arrangement%20in%20the%20largest%20democracy.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPM%20Modi%2C%20addressing%20an%20election%20rally%20at%20Harda%20under%20the%20Betul%20Lok%20Sabha%20seat%20in%20Madhya%20Pradesh%2C%20asked%20if%20voters%20were%20ready%20for%20%26quot%3Bfive%20prime%20ministers%20in%20five%20years%26quot%3B%20formula%20and%20called%20it%20a%20dangerous%20game%20by%20the%20opposition%20alliance%20in%20which%20the%20Congress%20is%20the%20biggest%20constituent.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20BJP's%20star%20campaigner%20doubled%20down%20on%20the%20Congress's%20alleged%20plan%20to%20redistribute%20wealth%20by%20what%20he%20called%20%26quot%3Bsnatching%20properties%20of%20people%26quot%3B%20and%20added%20that%20an%20advisor%20to%20the%20party's%20'shehzada'%20(a%20reference%20to%20Wayanad%20MP%20Rahul%20Gandhi)%20has%20now%20suggested%20imposing%20an%20inheritance%20tax.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20PM%20was%20referring%20to%20remarks%20by%20Sam%20Pitroda%2C%20president%20of%20the%20Indian%20Overseas%20Congress%20who%20has%20talked%20about%20the%20inheritance%20tax%20law%20in%20the%20United%20States%20while%20answering%20a%20query%20on%20the%20%26quot%3Bredistribution%20of%20wealth%26quot%3B%20issue.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20BJP%20stalwart%20said%20the%20Congress%20hates%20SCs%2FSTs%2FOBCs%20to%20such%20an%20extent%20that%20it%20wants%20to%20give%20reservation%20provided%20to%20them%20in%20jobs%20and%20education%20to%20its%20%26quot%3Bmost%20loved%20community%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20said%20while%20there%20is%20a%20clarity%20in%20the%20BJP%20over%20the%20leadership%20issue%2C%20the%20same%20is%20missing%20in%20the%20INDIA%20grouping.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BPeople%20should%20know%20to%20whom%20INDI%20alliance%20leaders%20want%20to%20hand%20over%20the%20reins%20of%20the%20country.%20It%20is%20clear%20in%20the%20BJP%20that%20it%20is%20Modi%2C%20but%20what%20about%20them%3F%26quot%3B%20he%20asked%20the%20gathering.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThere%20have%20been%20media%20reports%20that%20a%20discussion%20is%20going%20on%20among%20INDI%20alliance%20people%20over%20'one%20year%2C%20one%20PM'%20formula.%20That%20means%20one%20PM%20in%20one%20year%2C%20second%20PM%20in%20the%20second%20year%2C%20third%20PM%20in%20the%20third%20year%2C%20fourth%20PM%20in%20the%20fourth%20year%2C%20fifth%20PM%20in%20the%20fifth%20year...%20They%20are%20busy%20auctioning%20the%20PM's%20chair%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said%2C%20lashing%20out%20at%20the%20opposition%20bloc.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPM%20Modi%20advised%20people%20to%20be%20alert%20about%20these%20leaders%2C%20who%20he%20maintained%2C%20are%20daydreaming%20like%20'Mungerilal%20Ke%20Sapne'.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20noted%20the%20Congress%20can%20go%20to%20any%20extent%20to%20please%20its%20vote-bank%2C%20and%20spoke%20about%20%26quot%3Bwealth%20redistribution%20and%20inheritance%20tax%26quot%3B%20issues%20to%20lash%20out%20at%20the%20main%20opposition%20party.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIf%20anyone%20has%20more%20than%20one%20car%2C%20motorcycle%20or%20house%2C%20it%20will%20be%20confiscated%20if%20a%20Congress-led%20government%20assumes%20office%2C%26quot%3B%20PM%20Modi%20opined.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAsking%20people%20to%20vote%20for%20the%20BJP%2C%20PM%20Modi%20said%20their%20one%20vote%20has%20ensured%20that%20the%20Indian%20economy%20jumped%20from%20the%2011th%20spot%20to%20the%205th%20place%20in%20ten%20years%20and%20a%20grand%20Ram%20temple%20was%20built%20in%20Ayodhya%20after%20a%20wait%20of%20500%20years.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20PM%20maintained%20the%20Congress%20manifesto%20talks%20about%20religion-based%20reservation%20in%20jobs%20and%20education.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20Congress%20Chief%20Minister%20of%20Telangana%20has%20just%20said%20that%20he%20will%20ensure%20reservation%20for%20Muslims%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20PM%20emphasised%20that%20when%20a%20Congress-led%20government%20was%20formed%20at%20the%20Centre%2C%20they%20first%20introduced%20religion-based%20quota%20in%20Andhra%20Pradesh.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThen%20the%20Congress%20was%20not%20completely%20successful%20in%20its%20plan.%20But%20the%20Congress%20still%20wants%20to%20play%20that%20game%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20stated.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPM%20Modi%20said%20to%20dilute%20reservation%20for%20OBCs%20in%20Karnataka%2C%20the%20ruling%20Congress%20in%20the%20southern%20state%20has%20included%20Muslims%20under%20that%20category.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThis%20action%20of%20the%20Congress%20is%20an%20alarm%20bell%20for%20the%20OBC%20communities%20of%20the%20entire%20country%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20cautioned.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPM%20Modi%20pointed%20out%20that%20the%20Constitution%20makers%20had%20clearly%20decided%20that%20reservation%20cannot%20be%20given%20on%20the%20basis%20of%20religion.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThis%20was%20the%20basic%20spirit%20of%20our%20Constitution%2C%20but%20the%20actions%20of%20the%20Congress%20are%20against%20the%20basic%20spirit%20of%20the%20Constitution%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said%20while%20accusing%20the%20grand%20old%20party%20of%20constantly%20trying%20to%20erase%20B%20R%20Ambedkar's%20statute%20book%20and%20snatch%20reservation%20from%20SCs%2FSTs%2FOBCs.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20Congress%20wants%20to%20snatch%20reservation%20from%20SCs%2FSTs%2FOBCs%20and%20give%20it%20to%20its%20special%20vote-bank%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20independence%2C%20the%20biggest%20opposition%20to%20the%20Congress%20came%20from%20Ambedkar%2C%20the%20chief%20Constitution%20maker%20wh