Coffee%20Bar%20in%20Bengaluru.%20Having%20started%20with%20these%20four%20dishes%20in%201965%2C%20the%20place%20continues%20to%20serve%20them.%20The%20recipes%20are%20a%20constant%20here.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhen%20Narasimha%20Rao%20started%20the%20eatery%2C%20it%20was%20the%20coffee%20that%20was%20the%20main%20draw.%20At%20the%20time%2C%20snacks%20were%20sourced%20from%20the%20local%20bakeries.%20Eventually%2C%20the%20family%20began%20preparing%20South%20Indian%20items%20and%20customers%20swear%20by%20the%20%3Cem%3Echutney%3C%2Fem%3E%20that%20is%20said%20to%20be%20the%20glue%20that%20holds%20the%20menu%20together.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EEdited%20by%20Pranita%20Bhat%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1713794159000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F04%2FScreenshot-2024-04-22-170929-1713786011.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F%3Fp%3D347938%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Larger%20than%20the%20usual%20idlis%20and%20shaped%20like%20discs%2C%20the%20%E2%80%98thatte%20idlis%E2%80%99%20of%20Bengaluru%20have%20a%20fan%20following%20of%20their%20own.%20Here%20are%20eight%20places%20in%20the%20city%20for%20idlis%20and%20other%20South%20Indian%20breakfast%20staples.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22Krystelle%20Dsouza%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A12%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F347938%2Fbest-thatte-idlis-in-bengaluru-south-indian-breakfast-veena-stores-mavalli-tiffin-room-umesh-dosa-point%2F%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Too%20Much%20Sugar%20in%20%E2%80%98Cerelac%E2%80%99!%20Guide%20On%20How%20To%20Design%20a%20Healthy%20Food%20Plan%20For%20Your%20Baby%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EWhen%20your%20baby%20turns%20six%20months%20of%20age%2C%20it%20signifies%20a%20major%20milestone.%20It%20is%20the%20time%20for%20them%20to%20start%20solid%20foods%2C%20with%20most%20cultures%20having%20a%20ceremony%20to%20mark%20the%20occasion.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECelebrations%20aside%2C%20the%20weeks%20leading%20up%20to%20this%20milestone%20are%20filled%20with%20great%20confusion%20as%20parents%20read%20books%2C%20speak%20to%20family%20and%20friends%2C%20watch%20videos%20and%20consult%20doctors%2Fnutritionists%20about%20what%20they%20should%20offer%20to%20the%20child%20first.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20a%20mother%C2%A0%20to%20a%2015-month-old%2C%20I%20wonder%20what%20to%20feed%20my%20toddler%20daily%20and%C2%A0%20how%20to%20give%20him%20a%20balanced%20diet.%20Our%20anxiety%20increases%20when%20we%20see%20a%20variety%20of%20opinions%20from%20different%20doctors%20and%20nutritionists.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20numbers%20don%E2%80%99t%20lie%20and%20the%20rising%20obesity%20amongst%20children%20today%20underscores%20the%20need%20for%20the%20right%20nutrition%20for%20children.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20era%20of%20quick%20commerce%20and%20fast%20food%2C%20one%20might%20be%20tempted%20to%20buy%20packaged%20food%20and%20purees%20like%20cerelac%20for%20babies.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20a%20new%20report%20has%20unearthed%20shocking%20facts.%20A%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.publiceye.ch%2Fen%2Fmedia-corner%2Fpress-releases%2Fdetail%2Fsugar-for-nestle-not-all-babies-are-equal%5C%22%3E%20report%3C%2Fa%3E%20published%20by%20the%20Swiss%20organisation%20Public%20Eye%2C%20and%20the%20International%20Baby%20Food%20Action%20Network%20(IBFAN)%2C%20found%20that%20Nestle%2C%20the%20Swiss%20multinational%20food%20company%2C%20adds%20more%20sugar%20in%20infant%20food%20products%20in%20lower-income%20countries%2C%20including%20India.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20report%20states%20that%20its%20infant%20cereal%20Cerelac%2C%20intended%20for%20babies%20from%20the%20age%20of%206%20months%2C%20contained%202.7%20grams%20of%20added%20sugar%20per%20serving%20in%20India.%20The%20same%20Cerelac%20contains%20no%20added%20sugar%20in%20the%20UK%20and%20Germany.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20why%20is%20this%20important%3F%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIndia%20is%20seeing%20a%20rising%20trend%20in%20childhood%20obesity%2C%20with%2043%20lakh%20children%20in%20the%200-5%20age%20group%20identified%20as%20obese%20or%20overweight%20in%202023%2C%20according%20to%20a%20report%20in%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Hindu%3C%2Fem%3E.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20World%20Health%20Organisation%20(WHO)%20recommends%20that%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F310976%2Fharsha-vardhan-bengaluru-starts-lil-goodness-healthy-snack-brand-nutrition-booster%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eno%20added%20sugars%3C%2Fa%3E%20or%20sweetening%20agents%20should%20be%20used%20in%20food%20for%20children%20under%20the%20age%20of%20three%20to%20reduce%20the%20risk%20of%20obesity.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPackaged%20food%20items%20like%20Cerelac%20typically%20provide%20an%20easy%20option%20for%20parents%20and%20have%20been%20used%20for%20decades%20in%20India.%20Over%20the%20past%20few%20years%2C%20doctors%20have%20stopped%20recommending%20such%20cereals%20and%20instead%20ask%20parents%20to%20provide%20homemade%20healthier%20alternatives.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESo%20what%20do%20you%20offer%20your%20babies%20when%20they%20start%20solids%3B%20and%20later%2C%20to%20your%20picky%20toddlers%3F%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Better%20India%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20spoke%20to%20paediatricians%20and%20nutritionists%20to%20answer%20these%20burning%20questions.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EWhich%20solid%20food%20should%20you%20introduce%20first%20to%20your%20baby%3F%C2%A0%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFirst%20things%20first%2C%20you%20must%20start%20solids%20for%20your%20baby%20only%20at%20six%20months%20of%20age%20and%20not%20earlier%2C%20say%20experts.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhen%20you%20start%20solids%2C%20breast%20milk%20or%20formula%20remains%20the%20primary%20source%20of%20nutrition.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20idea%20is%20to%20let%20babies%20try%20a%20wide%20variety%20of%20foods%20slowly%20and%20introduce%20them%20to%20varied%20tastes.%20Start%20with%20single%20ingredients%20and%20give%20each%20food%20item%20for%20three%20days.%20You%20could%20give%20carrots%2C%20apples%2C%20bananas%20or%C2%A0%20papayas%20in%20pureed%20and%20mash%20forms.%20You%20can%20slowly%20introduce%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F298516%2Fengineer-quits-job-to-make-natural-baby-food-mixes-earns-lakhs-tummy-friendly-sridevi-ashala%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3Eragi%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20rice%20porridges%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20and%20%3Cem%3Emoong%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20%3Cem%3Emasoor%20%3C%2Fem%3Eand%20%3Cem%3Etoor%20dal%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Vidhya%20Ramasubramanian%2C%20Head%2C%20Department%20Of%20Nutrition%20at%20the%20SMSIMSR%20(Sri%20Madhusudan%20Sai%20Institute%20of%20Medical%20Sciences%20and%20Research).%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EStart%20by%20replacing%20one%20meal%20a%20day%2C%20preferably%20breakfast%2C%20and%20slowly%20introduce%20the%20second%20meal.%20Don%E2%80%99t%20fret%20if%20your%20baby%20just%20eats%20one%20or%20two%20spoons%20in%20the%20beginning.%20It%E2%80%99s%20not%20about%20them%20finishing%20the%20bowl%2C%20the%20idea%20is%20to%20teach%20your%20baby%20to%20eat%20food%20and%20enjoy%20it%2C%20stresses%20Vidhya.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EHere%E2%80%99s%20a%20sample%20meal%20plan%20for%20a%20toddler%20by%20Vidhya%20Ramasubramanian-%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F04%2F1-23-1713782385.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F04%2F1-23-1713782385.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebette