%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3E%20Hydroponic%20farming%20is%20an%20innovative%20and%20efficient%20way%20to%20grow%20crops%20without%20needing%20soil.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EFour%20problems%2C%20one%20solution%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFor%20the%20past%2013%20years%2C%20the%20BSc%20graduate%20has%20been%20growing%20traditional%20crops%20using%20conventional%20farming%20techniques.%20In%20fact%2C%20he%20used%20to%20grow%20strawberries%20on%20the%20open%20farm%20on%20five%20acres%20of%20land.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20process%20was%20very%20cumbersome%20as%20it%20required%20a%20lot%20of%20land%2C%20mulching%2C%20and%20drip%20irrigation.%20Weeding%20is%20also%20a%20common%20issue%20in%20growing%20strawberries%20on%20land.%20To%20get%20rid%20of%20the%20unwanted%20grass%2C%20we%20had%20to%20employ%20agricultural%20labourers.%20The%20labour%20charges%20alone%20would%20cost%20us%20Rs%2050%2C000%20to%20remove%20weeds%20from%20a%20%3Cem%3Ebigha%3C%2Fem%3E%20of%20land%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFor%20Dheeraj%2C%20hydroponics%20farming%20seemed%20a%20panacea%20for%20all%20challenges.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%202021%2C%20he%20went%20to%20Madhya%20Pradesh%20to%20undertake%20training%20by%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F336600%2Ftech-nursery-hydroponics-aeroponics-farming-ratlam-brothers-arbind-ravindra-dhakad%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EDhakad%20Brothers%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20learn%20the%20hydroponics%20method%20of%20cultivation.%20%E2%80%9CIn%20hydroponics%20farming%2C%20you%20give%20nutrients%20to%20plants%20via%20water.%20A%20crop%20requires%2013%20kinds%20of%20nutrients%20including%20primary%20nutrients%20like%20nitrogen%2C%20phosphorus%2C%20and%20potassium%2C%20secondary%20nutrients%20like%20calcium%2C%20sulphur%2C%20and%20magnesium%2C%20and%20tertiary%20nutrients%20like%20iron%2C%20zinc%2C%20manganese%2C%20copper%2C%20boron%2C%20molybdenum%2C%20and%20chlorine.%20These%20elements%20act%20as%20an%20essential%20catalyst%20for%20plant%20growth%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20explains.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CAlthough%20I%20knew%20the%20technique%20to%20give%20these%20nutrients%20via%20water%2C%20I%20did%20not%20know%20the%20ratio%20in%20which%20these%20elements%20were%20required%20to%20be%20given%20to%20the%20crop.%20The%20training%20helped%20me%20learn%20the%20approach%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F04%2Fstrawberry-3-1-1713533903.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Within%20two%20months%2C%20Dheeraj%20was%20able%20to%20harvest%205%20tonnes%20of%20strawberries.%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F04%2Fstrawberry-3-1-1713533903.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F04%2Fstrawberry-3-1-1713533903-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F04%2Fstrawberry-3-1-1713533903-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F04%2Fstrawberry-3-1-1713533903-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F04%2Fstrawberry-3-1-1713533903-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-347856%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EWithin%20two%20months%2C%20Dheeraj%20was%20able%20to%20harvest%205%20tonnes%20of%20strawberries.%20Photo%3A%20Pixabay.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3E5x%20more%20produce%20in%20small%20space%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EComing%20back%2C%20Dheeraj%20established%20a%203%2C500%20sq%20ft%20hydroponics%20set-up%20on%20his%20farm.%20Thereafter%2C%20he%20planted%209%2C000%20saplings%20of%20strawberries%20using%20coco%20peat%20as%20a%20medium.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20used%20grow%20bags%20and%20filled%20them%20with%20cocopeat.%20In%20these%20grow%20bags%2C%20I%20connected%20four%20drippers%20for%20water%20supply%20and%20made%20four%20small%20holes%20for%20drainage.%20Next%2C%20I%20planted%20the%20saplings%20and%20supplied%20all%20the%20nutrients%20to%20the%20crop%20with%20water.%20With%20this%20method%2C%20I%20water%20the%20plant%20at%20a%20gap%20of%20a%20week%2C%20instead%20of%20running%20the%20water%20supply%2024%C3%977.%20Almost%2070%20percent%20of%20water%20gets%20absorbed%20in%20the%20media%20for%20plant%20growth%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20took%20Dheeraj%201.5%20months%20and%20Rs%2012%20lakh%20to%20build%20the%20structure.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CBut%20it%20was%20all%20worth%20it.%20It%20is%20a%20one-time%20investment%20that%20reduces%20the%20overall%20input%20costs%20after%20a%20certain%20period.%20For%20five%20years%2C%20I%20do%20not%20have%20to%20worry%20about%20the%20maintenance%20of%20the%20system%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWithin%20two%20months%2C%20Dheeraj%20was%20able%20to%20harvest%205%20tonnes%20of%20strawberries%20and%20earned%20an%20income%20of%20Rs%203%20lakh%20in%20the%20same%20period.%20%E2%80%9CThis%20method%20is%20far%20better%20than%20conventional%20farming.%20With%20hydroponics%2C%20I%20got%20five%20times%20more%20production%20in%20hydroponics%20compared%20to%20open-land%20farming%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHighlighting%20the%20tasks%20farmers%20should%20be%20mindful%20of%20while%20adopting%20this%20method%2C%20he%20says%2C%20%E2%80%9CFarmers%20need%20to%20monitor%20the%20hydroponics%20farm%20at%20least%20once%20every%20day.%20The%20strawberries%20are%20heavily%20attacked%20by%20pests%20and%20fungus.%20In%20land-based%20farming%2C%20we%20were%20forced%20to%20spray%20chemical%20pesticides%20indiscriminately.%20But%20in%20hydroponics%2C%20I%20was%20able%20to%20cut%20chemical%20inputs%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F04%2Fstrawberry-2-1-1713533802.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Early%20this%20year%2C%20Dheeraj%20made%20sales%20of%20Rs%203%20lakh%20within%20two%20months%20by%20cultivating%20strawberries%20hydroponically.%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F04%2Fstrawberry-2-1-1713533802.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F04%2Fstrawberry-2-1-1713533802-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F04%2Fstrawberry-2-1-1713533802-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F04%2Fstrawberry-2-1-1713533802-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F04%2Fstrawberry-2-1-1713533802-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-347855%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EEarly%20this%20year%2C%20Dheeraj%20made%20sales%20of%20Rs%203%20lakh%20within%20two%20months%20by%20cultivating%20strawberries%20hydroponically.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFor%20this%2C%20he%20prepared%20a%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F338548%2Fmaharashtra-farmer-earns-huge-profits-by-growing-strawberry-farm-near-pune%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eunique%20fungicide%3C%2Fa%3E%20using%20curd.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIn%20one%20litre%20of%20curd%2C%20add%2050%20grams%20of%20copper%20wires%20or%20a%20copper%20%3Cem%3Elota%20%3C%2Fem%3E(spherical%20vessel).%20Keep%20the%20content%20for%20at%20least%2015%C2%A0%20days%20until%20the%20content%20becomes%20completely%20blue.%20Take%202%20ml%20of%20this%20mixture%20and%20dilute%20it%20in%201%20litre%20of%20water.%20Spray%20the%20diluted%20content%20on%20crops%20once%20every%20week%20throughout%20the%20season.%20This%20tackles%20fungi%20attack%20and%20gives%20a%20good%20yield%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20explains.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CAlthough%20I%20am%20extremely%20happy%20to%20reap%20benefits%20by%20adopting%20this%20new%20technique%2C%20initially%20I%20made%20some%20mistakes%20in%20getting%20good%20nutrients%20from%20the%20market.%20I%20got%20misled%20into%20buying%20nutrients%20from%20fraud%20companies.%20This%20delayed%20my%20production%20by%201.5%20months.%20But%20I%20am%20confident%20that%20I%20will%20be%20able%20to%20earn%20up%20to%20Rs%2010%20lakh%20in%20the%20next%20season%20from%20the%20same%20setup%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Dheeraj%2C%20who%20is%20currently%20cultivating%20red%20and%20yellow%20varieties%20of%20capsicum%20on%20the%20hydroponics%20setup.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EGiving%20his%20example%2C%20Dheeraj%20advises%20other%20farmers%20to%20explore%20hydroponics%20farming.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThis%20technique%20is%20not%20rocket%20science%2C%20any%20untutored%20farmer%20can%20reap%20handsome%20profits%20with%20hydroponics%20like%20me%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20suggests.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EEdited%20by%20Padmashree%20Pande.%20All%20photos%3A%20Dheeraj%20Verma.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1713767578000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F04%2Fstrawberry-1-1713533722.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F%3Fp%3D347819%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Encouraged%20by%20the%20soil-less%20farming%20technique%20used%20in%20Israel%2C%20Uttar%20Pradesh's%20Dheeraj%20Verma%20turned%20to%20cultivating%20strawberries%20using%20hydroponics.%20He%20earned%20Rs%203%20lakh%20in%20just%20two%20months.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22Shivani%20Gupta%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A8%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F347819%2Fstrawberry-farming-in-uttar-pradesh-hydroponics-farm-in-barabanki-earns-farmer-lakhs%2F%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Architect%E2%80%99s%20%E2%80%98Beehive%E2%80%99%20Cooling%20System%20is%20Affordable%20%26amp%3B%20Reduces%20Electricity%20Bills%20by%2065%25%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20scorching%20summer%20heat%2C%20the%20demand%20for%20energy%20peaks%2C%20increasing%20our%20electricity%20bills.%20While%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F281434%2Fagra-data-scientist-builds-solar-power-eco-friendly-air-conditioner-exalta%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eair%20conditioners%20%3C%2Fa%3Eand%20artificial%20coolers%20not%20only%20drain%20our%20pockets%20but%20also%20harm%20the%20environment.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDelhi-based%20Monish%20Siripurapu%20has%20come%20up%20with%20an%20affordable%20natural%20air%20cooler%20that%20not%20only%20keeps%20you%20cool%20in%20summer%20but%20also%20helps%20cut%20down%20on%20electricity%20bills%20by%20up%20to%2065%20percent!%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20architect%20has%20designed%20CoolAnt%20which%20harnesses%20the%20power%20of%20nature%20to%20keep%20spaces%20cool%20and%20comfortable.%20Interestingly%2C%20its%20terracotta%20design%20is%20inspired%20by%20the%20efficient%20cooling%20techniques%20of%20beehives%20and%20brings%20together%20sustainability%20and%20functionality%20in%20one%20package.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20system%20utilises%20terracotta%20cones%20arranged%20in%20a%20beehive%20pattern.%20Water%20is%20allowed%20to%20flow%20over%20the%20terracotta%20cones%20which%20acts%20as%20a%20natural%20cooling%20agent%2C%20absorbing%20heat%20from%20the%20surroundings.%20It%20then%20uses%20the%20process%20of%20evaporative%20cooling%20to%20release%20a%20gentle%2C%20refreshing%20breeze%20into%20the%20living%20spaces.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIt%20is%20the%20re-adaptation%20of%20traditional%20methods%2C%20combining%20ancient%20systems%20with%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F187517%2Flifestyle-eco-friendly-cooling-solution-without-ac-sustainable-homes-architect-india%2F%23google_vignette%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Emodern%20technologies%3C%2Fa%3E.%20We%20are%20opening%20buildings%20to%20nature%20instead%20of%20building%20installations%20for%20conventional%20urban%20structures%20that%20shut%20their%20inhabitants%20into%20these%20closed%20boxes%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Monish.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20startup%20observed%20that%20this%20structure%20can%20comfortably%20reduce%20the%20temperature%20up%20to%2030%20degrees%20Celsius.%20%E2%80%9CAt%20the%20factory%2C%20we%20reduced%20the%20temperature%20from%2045-47%20to%2032%20degrees%20Celsius%20because%20the%20water%20temperature%20was%2026-27%20degrees%20Celsius%2C%E2%80%9D%20informs%20Monish.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%202019%2C%20CoolAnt%20was%20among%20the%2012%20winners%20in%20the%20Asia-Pacific%20Low-Carbon%20Lifestyles%20Challenge.%20It%20bagged%20a%20%2410%2C000%20grant%20from%20the%20UN%20Environment.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3ELearn%20how%20CoolAnt%20is%20helping%20homes%20and%20commercial%20establishments%20reduce%20their%20power%20load%3C%2Fem%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-embed%20wp-block-embed-youtube%20wp-embed-aspect-16-9%20wp-has-aspect-ratio%5C%22%3E%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-embed__wrapper%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Cdiv%20data-origheight%3D%5C%22270%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22480%5C%22%20data-epautoplay%3D%5C%221%5C%22%20data-facadesrc%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fembed%2FQL-RhECqv_U%3Fenablejsapi%3D1%26amp%3Bautoplay%3D0%26amp%3Bcc_load_policy%3D0%26amp%3Bcc_lang_pref%3D%26amp%3Biv_load_policy%3D3%26amp%3Bloop%3D0%26amp%3Bmodestbranding%3D0%26amp%3Brel%3D0%