m%20an%20Apple%20device%2C%20the%20font%20will%20be%20from%20our%20Kohinoor%20series%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Satya.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIncidentally%2C%20the%20Kohinoor%20font%20family%20is%20on%20display%20permanently%20in%20London%E2%80%99s%20The%20Design%20Museum.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EThe%20inspirations%20and%20innovations%20driving%20ITF%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOne%20of%20the%20biggest%20challenges%20ITF%20faced%20was%20the%20scarcity%20of%20skilled%20type%20designers%20in%20India.%20Students%20and%20interns%20were%20trained%20and%20added%20to%20the%20team.%20Today.%20the%20team%20of%2025%20members%20are%20spread%20across%20the%20globe.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnother%20significant%20hurdle%20was%20cultivating%20a%20market%20for%20fonts.%20More%20people%2C%20including%20students%2C%20are%20now%20willing%20to%20invest%20in%20quality%20fonts%2C%20recognising%20their%20impact%20on%20the%20effectiveness%20of%20communication%20and%20branding.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20500px)%20100vw%2C%20500px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F04%2FITF-office-at-Ahmedabad_11zon-1713536350-500x500.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22500%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22ITF%20office%20at%20Ahmedabad%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F04%2FITF-office-at-Ahmedabad_11zon-1713536350-500x500.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F04%2FITF-office-at-Ahmedabad_11zon-1713536350-300x300.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F04%2FITF-office-at-Ahmedabad_11zon-1713536350-150x150.jpg%20150w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F04%2FITF-office-at-Ahmedabad_11zon-1713536350-768x768.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F04%2FITF-office-at-Ahmedabad_11zon-1713536350-1536x1536.jpg%201536w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F04%2FITF-office-at-Ahmedabad_11zon-1713536350-2048x2048.jpg%202048w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F04%2FITF-office-at-Ahmedabad_11zon-1713536350-96x96.jpg%2096w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-347887%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22500%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EITF%20office%20at%20Ahmedabad%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20prices%20of%20ITF%20fonts%20range%20from%20just%20Rs%202%2C500%20for%20a%20one-user%20desktop%20licence%20to%20several%20lakhs%20a%20year%20for%20a%20large%20enterprise%20licence.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CAt%20ITF%2C%20we%20offer%20free%20licences%20to%20students%20and%20teachers%2C%20aiming%20to%20support%20education%20and%20nurture%20the%20next%20generation%20of%20designers.%20In%202021%2C%20we%20launched%20%E2%80%98Fontshare%E2%80%99%2C%20providing%2025%25%20of%20our%20retail%20font%20library%20for%20free%2C%20to%20make%20high-quality%20fonts%20accessible%20to%20everyone.%20Fontstore%20was%20envisaged%20as%20a%20marketplace%20but%20currently%2C%20we%20sell%20only%20our%20own%20fonts.%20Quality%20and%20royalty%20are%20two%20issues%20that%20come%20up%20if%20we%20sell%20fonts%20developed%20by%20others%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20explains.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EApart%20from%20developing%20fronts%20from%20scratch%2C%20ITF%20also%20acquires%20fonts.%20Recently%2C%20it%20has%20acquired%20several%20independent%20foundries.%20%E2%80%9CWe%E2%80%99re%20on%20the%20cusp%20of%20launching%20a%20new%20umbrella-type%20foundry%20that%20will%20unite%20all%20our%20brands.%20Our%20goal%20is%20to%20expand%20our%20retail%20library.%20A%20key%20focus%20for%20us%20is%20ensuring%20our%20library%20is%20inclusive%2C%20representing%20not%20just%20English%20or%20Indian%20languages%20but%20also%20those%20that%20are%20endangered%20and%20less%20represented%20worldwide.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETalking%20about%2